title: Vietnam Quarantines Tens of Thousands in Coronavirus Camps
description: Vietnam has sent tens of thousands of people to quarantine camps in an effort to stem the spread of the Chinese coronavirus in the country, Reuters revealed on Thursday.
content:
Vietnam is forcing tens of thousands of people into quarantine camps to stem the spread of the Chinese coronavirus in the country, Reuters revealed on Thursday.
